cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with depth completion using LIDAR sensors. It could also belong to robotics (cs.RO) as it has applications in autonomous driving. Machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories are also likely as the proposed approach involves a multi-scale encoder-decoder network and sparsity-invariant operations.
